{{italic title}} [[File:Durer, madonna degli animali.jpg|thumb|280px]] The '''''Madonna of the Animals''''' is a c.1503 drawing on card by the artist [[Albrecht Dürer]], measuring 32&nbsp;× 24&nbsp;cm. Some areas of the drawing also feature watercolour. It is now held in the prints and drawings collection of the [[Albertina]] in [[Vienna]].
