'''Sienna X''' is a [[sunless tanning|fake tanning]] and wax company created in 2008, based in [[Worcester]], Worcestershire.<ref>[http://www.marieclaire.co.uk/news/539927/how-to-party-like-marie-claire.html How to party like Marie Claire!] 18 Dec 2012 "We made a stoic attempt at meeting deadlines and filing copy, all whilst dashing between hair appointments, courtesy of Evo Hair, and tanning sessions with James Harknett for Sienna X (even an MC gal needs a little help looking fabulous sometimes),"</ref> It is a subsidiary of The Spray Tan Cubicle Company, founded by Nicola Matthews in 2004.

